#: ../../P/pilot-error.rst:9
msgid ""
"[Sun: from aviation] A user's misconfiguration or misuse of a piece of "
"software, producing apparently buglike results (compare :ref:`UBD`\\). \"Joe"
" Luser reported a bug in sendmail that causes it to generate bogus "
"headers.\" \"That's not a bug, that's pilot error. His :code:`sendmail.cf` "
"is hosed.\" Compare :ref:`PEBKAC`\\, :ref:`UBD`\\, :ref:`idiot`\\."
msgstr ""
"[Sun:航空から]ユーザによるソフトウェアの設定ミスや誤用で、一見バグのような結果を生むもの(\\ :ref:`UBD`\\ と比較せよ)。「Joe "
"Luserがsendmailに偽のヘッダを生成させるバグを報告したんだ」「それはバグじゃない、pilot errorだ。彼の\\ "
":code:`sendmail.cf`\\ がめちゃくちゃなんだ」\\ :ref:`PEBKAC`\\ 、\\ :ref:`UBD`\\ 、\\ "
":ref:`idiot`\\ と比較せよ。"
